snippet.title: Devil Inside Us: Roots of Evil - Release Date Reveal Trailer | Switch, PS4/5 and Xbox One/Series S|X
snippet.description:
In Devil Inside Us: Roots of Evil, players take control of Aughust Heylel, a 74-year-old exorcist in the most terrifying case of his life. This first-person horror game launches on November 30, 2023 for Nintendo Switch, PS4, PS5, Xbox One, and Xbox Series S|X.
